-- Poland's Alior Bank buys 98 pct stake in Meritum Bank
-- By Marcin Goettig
-- Tue Oct 21, 2014 01:40AM EDT
-- None



WARSAW, Oct 21 (Reuters) - Poland's mid-sized lender Alior Bank <ALRR.WA> said on Tuesday it had agreed to buy a 97.9 percent stake in its smaller rival Meritum Bank from Innova Financial Holdings, WCP Cooperatief and the EBRD for a total of 353 million zlotys ($107 mln).

